.

1. *Nečim* se bavim proteklih nekoliko godina. (I have been dealing with something for the last few years.)
2. On je svoj život posvetio *nečemu* posebnom. (He dedicated his life to something special.)
3. *Nečim* me je iznenadio. (He surprised me with something.)
4. Nisam zadovoljan *nečim* u njegovom ponašanju. (I'm not satisfied with something in his behavior.)
5. Ovo je dokaz da se isplati verovati *nečemu*. (This is proof that it pays to believe in something.)